  "title": "Staff/Cashier for a Dim Sum Restaurant",
  "description": "<p>To apply or find out more, please contact</p><p><strong>Leong Jia Wei </strong>(Reg No: R25157456) on WhatsApp <strong>+65 80358497 </strong>or email <a href=\"mailto:jiawei@placement.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jiawei@placement.com.sg<br /><br /><br /></a>My client is a Teochew Dim Sum restaurant in the East, Singapore, hiring one <strong>staff / cashier</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Job duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Working hours: 0500-1700 daily. Off Day: Every Wednesday</li><li>Wrapping kueh, steaming kueh, packing kueh, and selling kueh</li><li>Answering phone calls, taking orders, and handling payments</li><li>Occasionally assisting with other kitchen duties</li><li>Some cleaning and hygiene-related tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Speaking English and Mandarin Chinese, to facilitate internal communication and communication with customers and stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>7 days of Annual Leave, with one additional day added each year.</li><li>Good performance will be rewarded with salary increments and a year-end bonus.</li><li>Breakfast is provided at the shop, and lunch is packed and provided by the company.</li></ul>",
